  line `THE ACTUARIES ACT, 2006`
  line __________________
  line `ARRANGEMENT OF SECTIONS`
  line __________________
  line `CHAPTER I`
  line `P RELIMINARY`
  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `1. Short title, extent and commencement.`
  line `2. Definitions.`
  line `CHAPTER II`
  line `I NSTITUTE OF A CTUARIES OF I NDIA`
  line `3. Incorporation of Institute.`
  line `4. Transfer of assets, liabilities, etc., of Actuarial Society.`
  line `5. Objects of Institute.`
  line `6. Entry of names in register.`
  line `7. Associates and fellows.`
  line `8. Honorary, affiliate and student members.`
  line `9. Certificate of practice.`
