  line `18. Resignation from membership and filling up to casual vacancies.`
  line `19. Functions of Council.`
  line `20. Staff, remuneration and allowances.`
  line `21. Committees of Council.`
  line `22. Finances of Council.`
  line `CHAPTER III`
